{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SorcererRise}}
'''A_SorcererRise'''<br />
(no parameters)

Clears the calling actor's SOLID flag and spawns in its place a {{Class|Sorcerer2}}, which is put in its Rise state. The spawned actor has the same friendliness settings as the calling actor.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Sorcerer1}} and derived classes.

